descriptionHtml:
[b]Players home.

[/b][b]ABC1[/b] has it's own world space.

Entrance to ABC1 "Portal Gem Door" is located at WHITERUN, go over the draw bridge then turn left into the passage,see picture for more info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

Cleaned with TES5Edit.

[b]Requirements:[/b] Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[b]Installation:[/b] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,
                     then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[b]Unistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.

[b]CREDITS:[/b] Many thanks to arrioch for his permission to use his "Arri's Snow Elf Ruins Retexture"
               Also a very big thank you to Varlaisaran for his Adabala Building System - Ayleid Transfusion,
               the detailing on the wall structure is brilliant.

My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
author: tanyferan
